1
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:44,320
That Li Guangming really is a piece of work.

2
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:46,159
Sending the child over so quickly.

3
00:00:57,479 --> 00:00:58,159
Bao'er.

4
00:00:58,159 --> 00:00:59,479
Mommy's here. Mommy's here.

5
00:00:59,479 --> 00:01:00,079
Don't cry.

6
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,560
You just threw the child to Li Guangming like that,

7
00:01:03,799 --> 00:01:04,840
and left by yourself?

8
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:05,879
Mom.

9
00:01:06,239 --> 00:01:07,480
You didn't see it.

10
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,879
That Li Guangming took my sister's money,

11
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:09,640
snatched it all away.

12
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:10,799
He even hit my sister.

13
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:18,239
Yingzhu.

14
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:21,079
Mom knows it's not easy for you.

15
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:24,079
But you still have to go back.

16
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:26,200
You're married to him now.

17
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:27,560
Mom.

18
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,000
My sister got beaten up.

19
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:29,879
And you still want her to go back?

20
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:31,120
What are you thinking?

21
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,879
Your sister always staying at her maiden home

22
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,400
isn't a solution either.

23
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,560
If people start spreading rumors that she's divorced,

24
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,519
then what do we do?

25
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,159
What would we say then?

26
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:40,519
We can't control what others say.

27
00:01:40,519 --> 00:01:41,599
Let them say whatever they want.

28
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:43,120
We just won't listen.

29
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:45,599
Gossip can kill.

30
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,879
This family...

31
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:48,599
She didn't give birth to a boy,

32
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:50,519
so her in-laws kicked her out.

33
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,519
When did this happen?

34
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:52,400
You didn't know?

35
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,079
I didn't know.

36
00:01:53,079 --> 00:01:53,719
This...

37
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,480
She gave birth to one child,

38
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,200
but became a mother of two.

39
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,359
I'm taking him away.

40
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,519
Yingrong, what are you doing?

41
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,719
That's for the Li family to raise.

42
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:04,599
It has nothing to do with you.

43
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,400
I'm sending him back.

44
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,159
Enough.

45
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:07,879
Don't cause more trouble.

46
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,479
Matters after marriage...

47
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:11,639
aren't something you can reason out clearly.

48
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:13,080
If you really care about your sister,

49
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,439
don't take matters into your own hands.

50
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,360
Come.

51
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,280
Give me a hand.

52
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:23,080
Come.

53
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,000
Hurry up.

54
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:29,120
You two...

55
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,919
neither of you gives me peace of mind like Third Sister.

56
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:31,840
Mom.

57
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:33,360
You don't know.

58
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,080
Wang Yingtang took the money and is out there...

59
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:36,800
What about Third Sister?

60
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,439
Forget it.

61
00:02:39,879 --> 00:02:41,080
You wouldn't believe me if I told you.

62
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:44,960
Get out.

63
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,680
Let your sister rest.

64
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:56,680
What are you doing?

65
00:02:57,639 --> 00:02:59,319
Bao'er and my sister took my room.

66
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:00,360
I'm sleeping in Yingtang's room.

67
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:01,360
No way.

68
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,080
Your Third Sister...

69
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,800
she doesn't allow anyone to touch her things.

70
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,120
She definitely won't let you sleep in her bed.

71
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,759
She's living at school.

72
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:08,000
This room is empty.

73
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,479
Why can't I sleep here?

74
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:11,639
You know your Third Sister's temper.

75
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:12,800
Don't provoke her.

76
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:14,280
Go, go sleep in my room.

77
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:15,719
Mom.

78
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:17,960
I'm not a child anymore.

79
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,520
I can't possibly sleep with you and Dad

80
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,000
in the same room.

81
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,280
Hurry up and go.

82
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:25,080
If your Third Sister comes back and sees you in her room,

83
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,560
she'll never let it rest.

84
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:27,120
Go.

85
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:27,680
Go.

86
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,960
Then where do you want me to sleep?

87
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,759
Sleep wherever you want.

88
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,719
Just not in here.

89
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:46,919
Stop right there

90
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:51,800
Come here

91
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:01,919
Sit down

92
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:07,120
Why are you running?

93
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,080
It's crowded

94
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:09,719
When we were kids, the six of us

95
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,680
all slept in this courtyard

96
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,719
How come it wasn't crowded then?

97
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,279
Thanks for helping my sister today

98
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,720
But

99
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,519
you slaughtered two of my pigs, didn't you?

100
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,519
It's only right to pay back debts, isn't it?

101
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:27,439
Yes

102
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:28,079
Good

103
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,959
Then I'll reluctantly

104
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,560
offer you a solution

105
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,720
Run the vinegar workshop with me

106
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,160
Li Guangming

107
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,040
Your salary

108
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,800
This isn't right

109
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,759
This is less than what I got before I became Director

110
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,720
What's going on?

111
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:59,560
The factory is struggling right now

112
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,720
It's good enough just to get a living allowance

113
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,759
I'm afraid when the layoff list comes out

114
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,879
if you're laid off, you'll only get the buyout compensation

115
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,000
and the layoff allowance

116
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,360
By then, you won't even have a job

117
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,600
How long can you last?

118
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,040
So

119
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:13,759
getting this living allowance is already very good

120
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,920
Try to understand the factory's difficulties

121
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,079
The factory has it hard?

122
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,399
I have it harder

123
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,120
How am I supposed to pay back that 500,000?

124
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,639
Come out with me later

125
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:35,839
I...

126
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,600
Wait

127
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,360
Come out with me to debug the machines

128
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:42,800
Director Li

129
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:44,879
Didn't you tell me to go move cement?

130
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,879
What skills do I have to fix any machines?

131
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:51,680
You dare disobey me?

132
00:05:54,879 --> 00:05:55,560
No

133
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,279
The 500,000 compensation

134
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,319
Even if I have to beg

135
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,040
I must make him go with me

136
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:06,000
Minjiang

137
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:06,759
Minjiang

138
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,279
Minjiang

139
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:09,720
Minjiang, wait for me

140
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:10,399
Minjiang

141
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:11,319
Minjiang

142
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:14,519
Director Li

143
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,000
With a cement mover like me

144
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,120
what is there to talk about?

145
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:21,360
You're so busy with work

146
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:23,680
aren't you afraid of wasting your time?

147
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,560
Minjiang

148
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:28,879
I've thought about it

149
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,439
I think that

150
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,199
moving cement

151
00:06:31,439 --> 00:06:32,959
is a waste of your talents

152
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:34,839
I'll transfer you back

153
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:35,839
And

154
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,800
I can even apply for a technical allowance for you

155
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,360
I actually quite like it over there

156
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,279
It's quiet and comfortable

157
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:45,639
And I don't have to

158
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:47,000
play politics with certain people

159
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,120
You...

160
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:08,600
Hey

161
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,199
We got paid today

162
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,199
Paying you back this much first

163
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:23,879
Haiyang said

164
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,600
besides slaughtering your two pigs

165
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,759
he also borrowed some money from you

166
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,639
I told you I'd give you time

167
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,879
You're like a clay idol crossing a river

168
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,839
you can't even save yourself

169
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,319
Take it

170
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,360
Don't end up selling yourself later

171
00:07:38,439 --> 00:07:39,160
to cover family expenses

172
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,319
Mom

173
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,360
Brother gave his wages to Wang Yingrong

174
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,199
What did you say

175
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,439
Your brother gave his wages to Wang Yingrong

176
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:00,240
Mom

177
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,399
I'm telling you this

178
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:02,519
but don't sell me out

179
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,160
This won't do

180
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:05,040
I'm going to find her and get the wages back

181
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,720
Why on earth

182
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,240
Why should I give it to the Wang family

183
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,040
Daring to take our family's wages

184
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,240
I'll settle the score with her

185
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:15,879
What are you doing

186
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:17,839
Ask your daughter what she did

187
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:19,759
She took our Minjiang's wages

188
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,199
Give us back our money

189
00:08:22,199 --> 00:08:23,399
That was your Haiyang

190
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:25,199
who slaughtered Yingrong's pig

191
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:27,360
Xiaochuan crashed her motorcycle

192
00:08:27,519 --> 00:08:28,519
That is what should be compensated

193
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,040
I even want to ask you to compensate us

194
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,079
for Jianshe's life

195
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,080
Have you compensated us

196
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,759
And you come asking us for money

197
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,320
How many years have you owed us

198
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:37,799
What did we say

199
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,480
Is there anyone who acts like you

200
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:40,759
That was

201
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,279
That was your Jianshe

202
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,679
who had a production accident

203
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,559
You should hold the factory responsible

204
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:46,799
It has nothing to do with our family

205
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:47,799
Nothing to do with your family

206
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,480
You saying this

207
00:08:48,559 --> 00:08:49,639
I feel ashamed for you

208
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,240
It really has nothing to do with your family

209
00:08:51,279 --> 00:08:52,360
That Xu Fugui of your family

210
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,279
living at that cement factory

211
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,519
why doesn't he dare to come back

212
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:55,879
It's just a guilty conscience

213
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,919
Today the factory pays wages

214
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:59,600
Your daughter took my son's wages

215
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,720
You give me yours

216
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:01,840
Mine

217
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:02,600
No

218
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,039
Get away

219
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,519
You Wang family want to bully us orphans and widows

220
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,399
It's not that easy

221
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,039
Pah

222
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,639
Who is bullying whom exactly

223
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,639
I'm so angry

224
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,759
You only know how to bully me

225
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:23,320
and say our family has no men

226
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,840
Auntie Chen took your wages away

227
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:27,120
She is just that kind of scoundrel and shrew

228
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:28,639
Now our family has no money

229
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,440
You hurry up and sell the motorcycle

230
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,600
Bring the money home

231
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,200
Mom

232
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:35,120
I really can't understand

233
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,519
You are so soft towards others

234
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:38,120
why are you so tough on me

235
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:39,480
You're really something

236
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,720
You can be tough on their family

237
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,600
and the result

238
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,600
Didn't you just cause a lot of trouble

239
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:45,559
If it weren't for you

240
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:47,000
would people point fingers behind our backs

241
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,440
and condemn us

242
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:49,240
Fine

243
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,519
I, as a daughter

244
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,320
have not done a single thing to satisfy you

245
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,840
I won't argue about this with you

246
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,919
You remember this for me

247
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,399
Our family has no boys

248
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:58,320
Only your sister can have a future

249
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:00,159
Your sister is about to take the college entrance exam

250
00:10:00,399 --> 00:10:01,879
Everything prioritizes her

251
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:03,639
You hurry up and exchange it for money

252
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:04,399
Give it to your sister

253
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:05,240
Fine

254
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:06,720
I will sell the motorcycle

255
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:08,519
But I'm not doing it for Wang Yingtang

256
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,799
I am doing it for myself

257
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:11,600
You

258
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:20,120
To get the vinegar workshop running,

259
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,759
we definitely need money.

260
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:24,600
I just hate to part with the motorcycle.

261
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:28,080
I had this bike repaired.

262
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,639
I really haven't ridden it much.

263
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:30,440
It's just like new.

264
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,519
Just help me sell it, please.

265
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,919
I told you last time.

266
00:10:33,919 --> 00:10:35,440
We don't sell second-hand bikes here.

267
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,519
Why don't you give it a try?

268
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,120
This really is just like new.

269
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,440
It's just that on the surface,

270
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,960
the paint is a bit worn.

271
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,679
The mechanic who fixed it, Engineer Zheng,

272
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,759
has excellent skills.

273
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,399
Look.

274
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,840
New bike quality,

275
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:46,879
used bike price.

276
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:48,840
You guys can still make a profit.

277
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:50,240
Boss, look.

278
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,440
She's hanging around here and won't leave.

279
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:53,559
Boss!

280
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:55,840
You said this bike was repaired by Engineer Zheng?

281
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:57,320
Is it Zheng Minjiang from the cement factory?

282
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,559
Yes, that's him.

283
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:00,639
He repairs all the machines in that factory.

284
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,799
Just for Engineer Zheng's skills,

285
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:04,000
I'll take this bike.

286
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:05,159
I won't lowball you either.

287
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:08,000
I'll give you ninety percent of the new price.

288
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:11,240
That's too generous, Boss.

289
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:14,320
You can just give me eighty percent.

290
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,519
Help me speak to Engineer Zheng.

291
00:11:16,519 --> 00:11:18,320
I want to invite him to my friend's factory

292
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,320
to help out.

293
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,399
To debug a batch of machines.

294
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:21,759
My friend's surname is Tang.

295
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:22,600
He's very wealthy.

296
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,759
Just consider it earning some extra cash.

297
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,720
Help pass the message.

298
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:25,840
No problem at all.

299
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,039
Then we have a deal.

300
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,440
Here is two thousand five hundred and twenty.

301
00:11:35,039 --> 00:11:36,320
Don't forget about our arrangement.

302
00:11:36,759 --> 00:11:37,240
Of course.

303
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:37,919
Okay, bye-bye.

304
00:11:37,919 --> 00:11:38,600
Thank you, Boss.

305
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,080
Good, good.

306
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:41,399
Let's go.

307
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,559
It's so dusty.

308
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,360
Why did you bring me here?

309
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:59,000
You said it yourself: debts must be paid.

310
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,360
So take this vinegar workshop

311
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:02,279
and clean it inside and out.
